 {"id": "bd-66l.1", "title": "Implement CI workflow matrix for build, tests, conformance, profiles, fuzz, embedded, and perf", "description": "Background:
Quality policy is only real when encoded in CI. Workflow structure must mirror plan-gate structure.

Subtasks:
- Define jobs for check, unit-invariant, conformance, profile-parity, fuzz-parity, embedded-matrix, perf-tail-deadline, and e2e scenario packs.
- Ensure deterministic artifact naming and retention.
- Ensure failure output is actionable and machine-readable where possible.
- Enforce publication of test run manifests and first-failure summaries for each test lane.

Acceptance Criteria:
- CI runs all required jobs on expected triggers.
- Job outputs are sufficient for triage without rerunning everything locally.
- No critical gate is left as manual-only.
- Missing e2e artifacts/manifests fail the workflow.", "notes": "2026-02-28: Completed CI workflow hardening for lane manifests/first-failure summaries and deterministic artifact naming. Updated .github/workflows/ci.yml and perf.yml: added per-lane machine-readable manifest emission (build/ci-manifests/*.manifest.json), e2e run_manifest publication enforcement, conformance/profile summary presence checks, fuzz/embedded artifact validation, lint-docs in check lane, deterministic artifact names using github.run_id/run_attempt. Verification via rch offload: make format-check, lint, build, test, conformance, profile-parity all PASS.", "status": "closed", "priority": 0, "issue_type": "task", "assignee": "FrostyPrairie", "created_at": "2026-02-27T00:51:00.106194478Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "updated_at": "2026-02-28T01:21:14.302625020Z", "closed_at": "2026-02-28T01:21:14.302597949Z", "close_reason": "Implemented CI/perf workflow matrix refinements, deterministic artifact naming, lane manifest + first-failure summaries, and manifest/artifact enforcement checks.", "source_repo": ".", "compaction_level": 0, "original_size": 0, "labels": ["ci", "gates", "workflows"], "dependencies": [{"issue_id": "bd-66l.1", "depends_on_id": "bd-1md.10", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-02T04:37:11Z", "created_by": "import", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-66l.1", "depends_on_id": "bd-1md.11", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-02T04:37:11Z", "created_by": "import", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-66l.1", "depends_on_id": "bd-1md.2", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-02T04:37:11Z", "created_by": "import", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-66l.1", "depends_on_id": "bd-66l", "type": "parent-child", "created_at": "2026-03-02T04:37:11Z", "created_by": "import", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-66l.1", "depends_on_id": "bd-ix8.3", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-02T04:37:11Z", "created_b